categories: Category:Missions of the Galactic Civil War

nodes.text: During the Galactic Civil War, a mission was carried out to the Selnesh Imperial Detention Center on the planet Selnesh, where the Rebel leader Gebnerret Vibrion was being held. The mission was undertaken by a commando team consisting of the Humans Koris Haslam, Melenna Seltrayne, Barsoulentinial Enkhet, Gowan Ch'lessan, Doctor Aurin Leith, and the Wookiee Liak.
